This work presents 35 easy to follow, original ideas, each with step-by-step instructions and diagrams. Jewellery designs include rings, bracelets, earrings and hair slides. Projects are assigned a skill-level, allowing readers with varying experience to pick and choose with confidence. Be inspired to express your personality through creative jewellery everyone will be envious about
